{"tid":2063721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喊「I can＇t breathe」挑釁洋記者 PTU遭訓示","createTime":"2020-06-14T08:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T12:53:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b616ab11b19ea48281c5e348b722fc70ac9166","tid":2063721,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/NFL5HOG44E6MQJ6SZKLZBI6ZBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FNFL5HOG44E6MQJ6SZKLZBI6ZBA%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=04f11f37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200614%2FNFL5HOG44E6MQJ6SZKLZBI6ZBA%2F&h=c8e164ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200614/NFL5HOG44E6MQJ6SZKLZBI6ZBA/</a><br />\n<br />\n喊「I can＇t breathe」挑釁洋記者 PTU遭訓示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】6.12一周年紀念活動中，有防暴警員向外籍記者呼喊「Black lives matter（黑人的命也是命）」、「I can't breathe（我無法呼吸）」等反警暴口號，似是嘲諷享有民主自由的美國同樣面對警暴。警方聲稱涉事警員其後遭訓示。立法會議員毛孟靜批評警員行為不專業及欠操守。<br />\n<br />\n根據facebook專頁「BeWater HK」上載片段，拍攝到防暴警員前晚在旺角山東街驅趕表演的樂隊時，一名行動呼號「PTU B4 3/5」的警員突然向着記者鏡頭不斷讀出美國反警暴示威的口號「Black lives matter」及「I can't breathe」，又說「There（Here） is not America（這裏不是美國）」。影片在各社交媒體廣泛流傳，網民對警員的表現都不明所以。<br />\n<br />\n看過影片的議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜批評警員行為失當：「unprofessional, unethical，不必要嘅一個姿態，面對記者，你做乜？除咗精神錯亂，冇其他解釋。」她認...................................但礙於擔心不獲續簽證而不敢投訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方承認有警員使用與其職務無關的字眼，表示關注，聲稱已訓示相關人員須注意個...................................層關注前線警務人員情緒失控問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6NKS27QJXYRGHSH5KZY7AWXNZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6NKS27QJXYRGHSH5KZY7AWXNZA.jpg&h=f2f8bf61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行動呼號「PTU B4 3/5」的防暴警前晚在旺角向記者鏡頭不斷大喊美國反警暴口號。「BeWater HK」片段截圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報記者遭警扯跌受傷<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：涉斬人 鄺星宇藏偉哥違毒藥例  民建聯李慧琼：反對一切暴力<br />\n<br />\n除了言語挑釁，本報記者前晚在銅鑼灣採訪時更遭警暴。當時已佩戴記者證的記者在崇光對出的電車........................推開記者，當記者配合警方後退時，突然有警員從後拉扯她的背包，記者隨即遭扯跌，膝蓋受傷，電話飛跌墮地損毀。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯前社區幹事鄺星宇前晚在觀塘同仁街涉持刀襲擊現場人士時，亦有警員向一名正在直播的記者企圖施襲，記者手機跌在地上，相機帶亦損壞。記協強.............................行兇動機。<br />\n<br />\n記協又指，警方在旺角朗豪坊、雅蘭中心外截查大批市民，不斷擴大封鎖線範圍，將記者由山...................述封鎖安排違反上月警方高層與新聞組織會面時的承諾，表示遺憾及失望。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張雅婷"},{"pid":"8ca9695d5ba5dc0c346055d3299a8837ee3ca605","tid":2063721,"uid":65604,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"訓示即係有職升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4cd1f0d2c9ad6641dd6295883653eef9859231","tid":2063721,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"繼續煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed71f77b38b300829b738386499bf8129eb4f5de","tid":2063721,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e4cd1f0d2c9ad6641dd6295883653eef9859231","tid":2063721,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"繼續煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T08:49:35.000Z","msg":"白左:我睇唔到"},{"pid":"e5f5c13154e766658136eef59fc7b28515676f68","tid":2063721,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">訓示</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e4cb956f7a25d69bf70603659d273479c6fec3ff","tid":2063721,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6fdca151b38e3b846d4a9ac44d873a075afed79","tid":2063721,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/J0qhprBk/NO-Justice-no-peace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FJ0qhprBk%2FNO-Justice-no-peace.jpg&h=109c7f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d04db4b7f457a62a7f82539e3a8adfa1c01a6b84","tid":2063721,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6fdca151b38e3b846d4a9ac44d873a075afed79","tid":2063721,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/J0qhprBk/NO-Justice-no-peace.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FJ0qhprBk%2FNO-Justice-no-peace.jpg&h=109c7f01&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236826fac0731b65fdd7958ef0e41dee1d96a1b8","tid":2063721,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"黑警+狗官+太監=曱甴集團"},{"pid":"0bb71f7cbd2bde487e7f5fbbb483289ae6d09ce4","tid":2063721,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:51:09.000Z","msg":"訓斥都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a99fb64816ebcb7b7e2701fab4c6d50504b779","tid":2063721,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"D英文屎到 there is not america <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}